<document xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
  xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/xdoc-2.0.xsd">
  <properties>
    <title>I18N Maven Plugin</title>
    <author email="opendj-dev@forgerock.org">ForgeRock AS</author>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="About I18N Maven Plugin">
      <p>
        A Maven plugin which generates I18N messages from property files.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section name="Goals Overview">
      <p>
        This plugin has two goals:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="generate-messages-mojo.html">i18n:generate-messages</a>
          : Goal which generates message source files from a one or more
          property files.
        </li>

        <li>
          <a href="clean-messages-mojo.html">i18n:clean-messages</a>
          : Goal which cleans unused messages files from a property file.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section name="Usage">
      <p>
        General instructions on how to use the I18N Framework, including this
        framework can be found on the <a href="../index.html">main page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
